## Output handling

- Default output is JSON (parseable). Pipe through `jq` for queries.
- Add `--pretty` for human-readable output.
- Add `--no-cache` to bypass the local SQLite mirror.

## Failure modes

- HTTP errors are emitted as `{"error": ..., "status": ..., "body": ...}` on stderr with exit code 1.
- Missing auth env vars typically yield 401 — check the auth section above.
